# screenfetch

> Display system information
> More information: https://github.com/KittyKatt/screenFetch

- Start screenfetch:

`screenfetch`

- Take a screenshot (requires 'scrot'):

`screenfetch -s`

- Specify distribution logo:

`screenfetch -A '{string value: distribution_name}'`

- Specify distribution logo and text:

`screenfetch -D '{string value: distribution_name}'`

- Strip all color:

`screenfetch -N`
